      "comment": "BERSERKER VIKING (8) flew the lids from the middle with a slick turn of foot before finishing second (25.46) and beaten 3.5 lengths over 450m at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to feature in the finish again. PAW NIALL (4) was in the money last time at this track (25.58) in a Grade 5, finishing a 3 length second. Has already won two times from this draw. Can hit the frame with the right run. PAW REVY (6) led throughout to score two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 5 length 4th at Bendigo (24.09). One of the better chances. WHODAT WHISKEY (2) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
